profile:
Urban Classic Cabinetry & Design, Inc. Designs, Manufactures, and Installs Fine Custom Cabinetry for residential and commercial uses, including Closet Organizers and all home storage.
Our product line ranges from affordable entry-level cabinetry to high-end, truly custom millwork, without limitations. Our designs have used popular themes such as Ornately Traditional and Ultra Modern Euro in collaboration with your vision to fulfill your highest expectations. We believe attention to functional accessories provide seamless and enjoyable daily experiences combining beauty in form and function.
Many people are broadening their Green Lifestyle to include environment friendly kitchen components. We have a wide array of eco-friendly products and materials readily available to satisfy your needs at any level. Going Green doesn't limit design or beauty.
We work closely with Homeowners, Builders, other Renovators, Interior Designers and Architects. The Canadian Home Builder Association Tommie Awards has recognized four recent projects Excellence in Design and Implementation.
Urban Classic welcomes the opportunity to manage your complete residential or commercial project. Our key personnel have a wealth of experience in construction and home renovations. We have an extensive list of project partner trades to engage in your project. These detail oriented individuals have time and again proven themselves capable, talented, and dependable. We love to manage projects because, ultimately the home's cabinetry is its Crowning Jewel and with our professional team we ensure all work on-site to be of a standard worthy of our cabinetry.
Please call for detailed information on making your vision a reality, and to view our portfolio of realities many have already experienced.
Contact Urban Classic Cabinetry & Design, Inc.
P: 250.860.2801
F: 250.860.2806
